'''布雷克·斯基勒魯普'''（{{bd|1985年|6月13日|}}）是一位[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]男子[[短道競速滑冰|短道競速滑冰]]選手。代表紐西蘭參加[[2010年冬季奧林匹克運動會|2010年冬季奧林匹克運動會]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vancouver2010.com/olympic-short-track-speed-skating/athletes/blake-skjellerup_ath1017200pQ.html |title=Vancouver 2010 Profile |accessdate=2013-12-11 |archive-date=2010-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100408234620/http://www.vancouver2010.com/olympic-short-track-speed-skating/athletes/blake-skjellerup_ath1017200pQ.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成績為第16名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/winter-olympics/3356627/Blake-Skjellerup-struggles-with-skating-pace|title=Blake Skjellerup struggles with skating pace|work=New Zealand Press Association|publisher=Stuff.co.nz|date=2010-02-22|accessdate=2010-05-09|archive-date=2012-05-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67RXbBgUp?url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/sport/winter-olympics/3356627/Blake-Skjellerup-struggles-with-skating-pace|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==運動生涯==
他目前正努力的準備參加在[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[索契|索契]]所舉行的[[2014年冬季奧林匹克運動會|2014年冬季奧林匹克運動會]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=About Blake |url=http://www.blakeskjellerup.com/Site/About_Blake.html |publisher=BlakeSkjellerup.com |year=2011 |accessdate=2012-01-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305065204/http://www.blakeskjellerup.com/Site/About_Blake.html |archivedate=2016年3月5日 }}</ref>2013年8月26日，斯基勒魯普在Indiegogo推出[[群眾募資|群眾募資]]以募得15000美元為目標，以幫助自己取得2014年冬季奧運會的參賽資格。募捐超過了最初的目標，最終募到29357美元。<ref>{{cite web |title=Send out gay speed skater Blake Skjellerup to the World Cup and Olympics |url=http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/send-out-gay-speed-skater-blake-skjellerup-to-the-world-cup-and-olympics |publisher=www.indiegogo.com |year=2013 |accessdate=2013-08-26 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119032203/https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/send-out-gay-speed-skater-blake-skjellerup-to-the-world-cup-and-olympics |dead-url=no }}</ref>

斯基勒魯普現在居住和訓練都在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[卡加利|卡加利]]。<ref name="VS" />

==個人生活==

斯基勒魯普在2010年5月接受澳洲雜誌DNA採訪時[[出櫃|出櫃]]，他說在[[2010年冬季奧林匹克運動會|溫哥華冬運]]後公開是為了讓大家把焦點放在他的比賽表現上，和避免嚇跑潛在的贊助商。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvnz.co.nz/othersports-news/kiwi-olympian-reveals-he-gay-3521126|title=Kiwi Olympian reveals he is gay|work=New Zealand Press Association|publisher=Television New Zealand|date=2010-05-06|accessdate=2010-05-09|archive-date=2010-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100509061132/http://tvnz.co.nz/othersports-news/kiwi-olympian-reveals-he-gay-3521126|dead-url=no}}</ref>他是少數公開同志身份參加奧運的選手，據報告他的男朋友也是運動員。<ref name=VS>{{cite news |url=http://www.vancouversun.com/life/Zealand+Olympian+Blake+Skjellerup+embraces+coming/3351683/story.html#ixzz1naJqteh1 |title=New Zealand Olympian Blake Skjellerup embraces coming out |date=2010-08-02 |work=Vancouver Sun |author=Zacharias, Yvonne |accessdate=2012-02-26 |archive-date=2018-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181029075639/http://www.vancouversun.com/life/Zealand+Olympian+Blake+Skjellerup+embraces+coming/3351683/story.html#ixzz1naJqteh1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://outsports.com/jocktalkblog/2010/05/05/new-zealand-olympian-comes-out/ |title=New Zealand Olympian comes out |work=Out Sports |accessdate=2012-01-15 |author=Buzinski, Jim |date=2010-05-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120124014936/http://outsports.com/jocktalkblog/2010/05/05/new-zealand-olympian-comes-out/ |archivedate=2012年1月24日 }}</ref>

